messages.text: I have to tell you something
OMG. You will not believe what happened last night
Ok you first
no, you
Ok. So. Anders texted me.
What happened to 3 weeks?
That’s what I said. Guess he was worried about me…
Anyway, he had me go into this classroom in the science building through a secret entrance
secret entrance???
That’s not the craziest part
The room was lined with tanks of reptiles. Snakes. Lizards. Frogs.
Frogs are amphibians
ok know-it-all
so he made me
how can I explain this without sounding utterly insane
he made me communicate with a snake
uh
I know. But you have to believe me, it just kind of came naturally.
This noise in the back of my throat
maybe I’m losing it. But the snake looked at me, and said something back.
Right. What did it say?
Just basically acknowledged my existence in its own snake way
anyway THEN I realized that I was locked in the room.
You know how the doors in that building can only be unlocked from the outside?
Total fire hazard.
Yeah, well these FEMA guys came in in their hazmat suits
I really thought I was done for.
I hid behind a desk and prayed that they wouldn’t see me
Then I noticed the snake I’d “talked” to slithering past me
And a lizard
and a frog
and I realized that ALL the reptiles (and amphibians) had broken loose
They were moving quickly towards the FEMA guys
first the guys tried to swat them off but there were too many
The snakes were crawling into their suits and stuff
They both fell to the ground and I got the hell out of there
and this is what I feel bad about. I shut the door behind me
Those guys are creeps. I’m sure they got what was coming to them
Am I going crazy?
Is this how it starts?
you aren’t going crazy.
I’m supposed to meet Anders later tonight.
I don’t know what to believe anymore.
He said some pretty out-there stuff...
Anyway. What was it you wanted to tell me?
Well, I did some snooping around Anders’s room
His idiot roommate left the door unlocked and I couldn’t help myself
and???
I found this in his trash
what is it
that’s what I’m trying to figure out
!!! What do those x’s mean??
Charles is dead, we know. Do we know a Janet?
Janet Marcusi.
I have Comp with her
*had
I think I saw something on fb about her being a meningitis victim
there were more of these
With other members of Anders’s clique of bio nerds in the middle
Whatever it is people are getting...
it’s being spread by Anders and his friends.
They’re the ones who started it.
That’s what I gleaned from the notebook I found shoved in the trashcan
And I think anders was right about those pills
He wasn’t just being paranoid
The question is this: what the hell are they spreading? And HOW?
He told me that they’d created a human/reptile mutation that was sexually transmitted
wtf. So those are people he hooked up with
that is not what I was expecting
it explains my symptoms
I was going to keep this from you, but here goes
How long has your hand been like that???
since I woke up this morning. It’s so gross
It’s not that bad. Cute mani!
don’t lie
Anyway he also told me that the FEMA guys are actually FBI...
and they’re trying to end the mutation by killing us with those pills
I had no idea I was part of some calculated plan though. Some…web
Like an idiot, I thought he actually slept with me because he liked me
one thing doesn’t add up
You said you took the pills
And yet you’re fine
I’m so sorry M
It’s just what he was telling you sounded so insane.
I wanted you to get better.
I really thought those pills would make you better
I could have DIED
It came from a good place, I promise
So stupid
UGH. Why can’t people just tell the TRUTH???
I’m really really really really sorry
I need some space, k?
I can help you. We can help each other
Not now. I’ll text you later
2 HOURS LATER
Melanie Fulbright?
Ok 2 hours is not space!!
And why the heck are you calling me by my full name?
This is Agent Frank Pearson, FBI.
We have your friend Sasha Penkov in holding and we need to ask you a few questions.
What? Holding? What does that mean?
I highly recommend that you meet with us.
If you decline we may have to resort to drastic measures.
Sasha, is this you?? Are you messing with me?
Ms. Penkov is in holding.
If you want to see her again, you’ll meet an agent at 2 a.m. tonight, at the East Gate.
Sasha, I swear, if you’re pulling my leg…
is that a confirmation?
Yeah, fine, whatever. Who needs to sleep anymore around here anyway?
We will see you at 2 a.m., Ms. Fulbright.
I’ll bring a 6 pack and some popcorn. We’ll make a night of it.
Please come alone and do not bring any food or alcohol
it was a JOKE
Noted. I’m switching Sasha’s mobile off now
See you soon!!!
asshole
